AC1:

Given that the SR hub has been successfully deployed in a CWA component

When I access the CWA Spending Rewards tool via the mobile app (NGA)

Then the CWA SR hub should launch within the mobile app

And the CWA SR hub should open in the default section - (Your offers)

And the default view should display the access to my ACTIVE offers

 

AC2:

Given that I have accessed the CWA Spending Rewards tool via the mobile app (NGA)

And the CWA SR hub has been launched within the mobile app

And the CWA SR hub has opened in the default section - (Your offers)

And the access to my active offers is clearly displayed in the default section

When I trigger the access to my active offers

{color:#333333}Then the Active Offers section should open in the "All Offers" view – (default view){color}

{color:#333333}And the "All Offers" view should display a SECTION TITLE (e.g. Active Offers){color}

{color:#333333}And the Section Title should include the TOTAL NUMBER of ALL active offers{color}

{color:#333333}And the "All Offers" view should display the SR offer category filters{color}

{color:#333333}And the SR offer category filters should include a filter titled "*All offers*"{color}

{color:#333333}And all other offer category filters should display the TITLE of their SR offer category{color}

{color:#333333}And each offer category filter should display the NUMBER of offers they hold{color}

{color:#333333}And the DEFAULT state of the "*All offers*" filter should be ACTIVE{color}

{color:#333333}And the DEFAULT state of all other filters should be INACTIVE{color}

{color:#333333}And the "All Offers" view should display a logo for each active offer{color}

{color:#333333}And each active offer logo should display the date the offer active{color}

{color:#333333}And each active offer logo should display an option to VIEW details of the offer{color}

 

{color:#333333}AC3:{color}

Given that I have accessed the CWA Spending Rewards tool via the mobile app (NGA)

And the CWA SR hub has been launched within the mobile app

{color:#333333}And I am in the All Offers view of the Active Offers Section{color}

{color:#333333}And all the offer category filters are displayed{color}

{color:#333333}When I click on ANY of the displayed filters (except "All Offers"){color}

{color:#333333}Then the Active Offers section view should change to the selected filter view{color}

{color:#333333}And the state of the selected filter should switch from INACTIVE to ACTIVE{color}

{color:#333333}And the state of the "All Offers" filter should switch from ACTIVE to INACTIVE{color}

{color:#333333}And the enabled filter view should display the SECTION TITLE (e.g. Active Offers){color}

{color:#333333}And the Section Title should include the TOTAL NUMBER of ALL active offers{color}

{color:#333333}And the enabled filter view should display a logo for each active offer{color}

{color:#333333}And each active offer logo should display the date the offer active{color}

{color:#333333}And each active offer logo should display an option to VIEW details of the offer{color}

{color:#333333} {color}

